00:00:29,090 --> 00:00:32,420
how do I know who I like the most? Hi, Joey.
我怎么知道要最喜欢谁呢？ 嗨，乔伊

11
00:00:33,960 --> 00:00:35,930
It pays nothing. It's an internship.
没有薪水，是实习的工作

12
00:00:36,130 --> 00:00:38,000
We have interns at Days of Our Lives.
《我们的日子》也有实习生

13
00:00:38,230 --> 00:00:41,260
Right. So it'll be the same, except less sex with you.
没错，所以是一样的东西 不同的只是不用常跟你上床

14
00:00:43,270 --> 00:00:45,360
What do you think they'll have you do there?
你觉得你去那里要做什么呢？

15
00:00:45,610 --> 00:00:48,740
It's a training program, but they hire the people they like.
这只是个训练课程 但是之后他们会聘请他们喜欢的人

16
00:00:48,940 --> 00:00:51,880
- That's great! - There's gonna be some grunt work..
-太棒了！ -一定会有些无聊乏味的工作让人讨厌

17
00:00:52,050 --> 00:00:55,680
which will stink. A grown man getting people coffee is humiliating.
一个大男人帮大家端咖啡真是羞辱

18
00:00:58,620 --> 00:01:01,560
Humiliating and noble.
羞辱，却高贵

19
00:01:02,120 --> 00:01:04,020
Thank you.
谢谢你

20
00:01:05,690 --> 00:01:07,850
You know, if I didn't already have a job..
如果我不是早有工作了

21
00:01:08,030 --> 00:01:10,120
I would've been good in advertising.
我应该会在广告业做得很好的

22
00:01:10,330 --> 00:01:13,030
Ross, you did not come up with: "Got Milk?"
