Where's Chandler? I want to wish him good luck on his first day.
钱德呢？ 我想要祝他第一天上班愉快

27
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:16,260
And I smelled bacon.
而且我也闻到培根香了

28
00:02:16,930 --> 00:02:19,660
- He just left. - Who did?
-他才刚走 -谁才刚走？

29
00:02:21,500 --> 00:02:23,970
Joey, you're never gonna believe it! She called!
乔伊，你不会相信的！她打来了！

30
00:02:24,170 --> 00:02:25,730
- She did? - You got it!
-是吗？ -你得到了！

31
00:02:25,870 --> 00:02:27,540
- I did? - What is she talking about?
-是吗？ -她是在说什么呢？

32
00:02:27,780 --> 00:02:29,970
I don't know, but it sounds great!
我不知道，但是听起来倒是挺棒的！

33
00:02:30,150 --> 00:02:32,310
Your agent called. You got that audition!
你的经纪人打电话来 你得到试演的机会了！

34
00:02:32,510 --> 00:02:33,850
- With Leonard Hayes? - Yes!
-跟李奥海斯吗？ -是的！

35
00:02:34,020 --> 00:02:37,710
Oh, my God, that is great! It's for a play on Broadway.
我的天啊，太棒了！ 这是百老汇的一出戏

36
00:02:37,890 --> 00:02:42,020
And in a real theater. Not that little one underneath the deli like last time.
在一间真的剧院，而不是像上次一样 是在快餐店下面的那种

37
00:02:42,260 --> 00:02:43,850
- Is it a good play? - It must be.
-是一出好戏吗？ -肯定是的

38
00:02:44,030 --> 00:02:47,620
I read it and didn't understand a single word!
因为我读了剧本 而且根本连一个字都看不懂！

39
00:02:47,830 --> 00:02:50,530
- Leonard Hayes is starring in it. - Yeah, and directing.
-李奥海斯也会参与演出 -是啊，兼导演

40
00:02:50,770 --> 00:02:53,200
He was so good in that movie of Macbeth.
